item.title: A Face In The Moon
item.description: I’m impressed, iPhoto’s facial recognition software can also id the moon. I mean, I have always known that there was a man on the moon and that when it was full there was an eye and nose that are clearly visible so I guess it would be a good training object.Is This The Moon?
